== Notes ==
=== Changi Museum ===
*Location: 1000, Upper Changi Road North.
*Opening hours: 9:30am - 5:00pm daily
*Bus: Take bus No. 2 from Tanah Merah MRT Station (EW4) or bus No. 29 from Tampines MRT Station (EW2)
*Remarks: Alight at the bus stop at the Changi Museum. Photography is not allowed within the Museum. 

